                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirement</strong> The greater shadow hit a living creature with a shadow hand Strike on its previous action.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The greater shadow pulls at the target's shadow, making the creature @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} or enfeebled 3 on a critical hit. This is cumulative with other @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled} conditions from shadows, to a maximum of @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 4}. If this increases a creature's @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled} value to 3 or more, the target's shadow is separated from its body (see shadow spawn). @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled} from Steal Shadow decreases by 1 every hour.</p>"
